{"name":"Heal Golem","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>Your golem companion is targeted by a spell or magical effect that deals its warded energy damage. Your golem companion need not actually take this damage for this reaction to trigger.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You invert the oncoming magic to heal your golem companion. Your golem companion regains 4d8+4 Hit Points. It then takes damage normally (if any) from the triggering effect.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The amount of healing increases by 1d8+1.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"heal-golem","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["healing"],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":4},"spellType":{"value":"heal"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"transmutation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":null,"time":{"value":"reaction"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{"MhfHMTxFQ599gvTv":{"value":"4d8+4","type":{"value":"","categories":[],"subtype":""},"applyMod":false}}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"heightening":{"type":"interval","interval":1,"damage":{"MhfHMTxFQ599gvTv":"1d8+1"}}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.3G1bPNYkmOXOAGtV"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686123612892,"modifiedTime":1686125220442,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"8Y6RIXIAaWWil9SI"}
{"name":"Golem Strike","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You channel a cantrip through your golem companion’s strike. Choose one of your cantrips that takes 1 or 2 actions to cast and requires a spell attack roll. The effects of the spell don't occur immediately but are imbued into your golem companion’s attack instead.</p>\n<p>Your golem companion makes a melee Strike with an unarmed attack.</p>\n<p>Your spell is coupled with their attack, using their attack roll result to determine the effects of both the Strike and the spell. This counts as two attacks for your multiple attack penalty, but you don't apply the penalty until after your golem companion has completed the golem strike. This spell follows the details under @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.KVj5ofUwu3VJSrVw]{Spellstrike} Specifics.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"golem-strike","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":4},"spellType":{"value":"attack"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"evocation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":true},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":null,"time":{"value":"2"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":null},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.zLHY0I78iU2iAf5w"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686123612892,"modifiedTime":1686125220445,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"OE1NCLeV0uBflpOP"}
{"name":"Golem’s March","type":"spell","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You send your golem companion forth on a devastating march. Your golem companion Strides up to their Speed.</p>\n<p>Each creature whose space they move into must attempt a Fortitude save. The results depend on your spellcasting tradition. If you have multiple traditions, choose one when you cast this spell. </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Arcane</strong>. On a failure, the creature is damaged as if hit by your golem companion’s unarmed attack (double damage on a critical failure).</li>\n<li><strong>Divine</strong>. On a failure, the creature takes a -1 status penalty to AC and Reflex saves until the end of your next turn (-2 status penalty on a critical failure).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.magic-specializations-effects.ioEXeBwk8pRX3sxZ]{Spell Effect: Golem’s March (Divine)}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.magic-specializations-effects.OrVdLaDq0G8EuXi4]{Spell Effect: Golem’s March (Divine, Critical Failure)}</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Occult</strong>. On a failure, the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1} for their next turn (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 2} on a critical failure).</li>\n<li><strong>Primal</strong>. On a failure, the creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.eIcWbB5o3pP6OIMe]{Immobilized} until the start of your next turn. On a critical failure, they take a -1 status penalty on checks to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.SkZAQRkLLkmBQNB9]{Escape}.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.magic-specializations-effects.nvohbhHlPgcX08DM]{Spell Effect: Golem’s March (Primal, Critical Failure)}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"golems-march","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"uncommon"},"level":{"value":2},"spellType":{"value":"save"},"category":{"value":"focus"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"transmutation"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":true,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":null,"time":{"value":"1"},"duration":{"value":""},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"fortitude","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/spell.svg","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.NSWFV9tIcd1VbtIm"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686123612892,"modifiedTime":1686125365900,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"hDVVGEVs1KjbCdRg"}
